Full Description: What is Teamitt?  Teamitt helps companies to unleash the passion of employees along with helping employees realize their purpose at work leading to innovation needed to stay competitive in ever-changing and challenging global markets. In the current existing models motivating employees lies in the hands of their immediate managers. As we all know not every manager can be an expert in the art and science of motivating employees and even if they are, it is not humanly possible for any manager to motivate all employees on a daily basis and in a consistent manner.  The goal of Teamitt is to help turn this inefficiency into business profits by unleashing the untapped human potential in the workforce.  The best way to motivate employees is to show seamlessly, in real-time how their day-to-day operations are impacting the business goals of the company in an easy to participate, simple to engage and fun to learn environment. Teamitt helps to achieve this seamless integration. Engagement for innovation through gamification Engagement at work perpetuates creative ideas and innovative insights. Teamitt help create an engaging environment by infusing simple games into daily operations of employees. Receiving another work email is not as boring and mundane anymore. Mobile and Peer-to-Peer knowledge sharing and learning Company knowledge, operational insights are gained by employees and stored in employee brains. Teamitt makes it easy for employees to make that wealth of knowledge available to other employees in the company by incentivizing them with more visibility within the company. This knowledge sharing caters to the mobile workforce by making needed learning available from any devise at all times.  Intelligent platform for operational efficiency Teamitt is an intelligent platform. It learns patterns among employees and patterns among projects. This intelligence can be applied for operational efficiency. Fresh, relevant and insightful company portal It is the dream of every company management that employees spend time on company portal. Teamitt helps to make this reality by keeping the company portal filled with content and information that is fresh, relevant and insightful in real-time. Employee personal goals center Teamitt comes with employee personal goals center making employees feel valued by the company resulting in building employee centric culture. Employees can create, track and achieve their personal goals leading to employees associating workplace with their personal achievement and personal wellbeing. Data driven and metric driven Measurement makes informed decisions possible. Teamitt measures and provides metrics for all the activity taking place on the platform.

Description: FirstChoice Hiring is a recruitment platform helping job seekers.
Headquarters Regions: Greater Atlanta Area, East Coast, Southern US
Full Description: FirstChoice set out to simplify and improve the hiring process. This was a time when “advanced” hiring services were using personality tests, which they knew were gimmicky and outdated. So, they hit the books, talked to psychology professors, and crafted one of the most accurate behavioral tests; a patented assessment that can gauge an applicant’s success in your company with 92% accuracy! That’s unheard of to this day, but they weren’t done yet. While many hiring agencies were transitioning to automated call systems, they did the opposite. They actually hired more account managers, because no one likes to talk to a robot. These same agencies began providing platforms where their customers actually have to design and post the job ads themselves… not us! Once again, they went against the grain and decided to handle everything for their clients ourselves. This is when Happy Hiring came to life. From job ad creation, to applicant assessments, posting jobs, to organizing candidate resumes… they do everything for their clients. So, if you’re ready to save time and money, while retaining the best employees, their Happy Hiring solution is the answer you’ve been looking for.

Driving to San Francisco in a red convertible while listening to Lana Del Rey and wearing Raybans. Relaxing on the beach, Havaianas, a straw hat and The Old Man and The Sea. The band will then have to pay back the advance thru CD, merch sales, etc. before the band will see any profits for themselves. With Faneebo, bands can set up and run their own Fan Club which will act as their own personal record label run by the band and in turn will allow fans to gain access to premium content while at the same time providing bands with the needed funds to help record, tour, buy merch, and more in which the bands won't have to worry about paying back.
